Package: claude-desktop
Version: 0.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: electron, libgtk-3-0, libnotify4, libnss3, libxss1, libxtst6, xdg-utils
Maintainer: shubham151 <shubham.cmishra@gmail.com>
Description: Claude Desktop for Linux (unofficial repackage)
 Unofficial Linux repackage of Anthropic's Claude Desktop built by
 repacking the official macOS application with a Linux-compatible
 native bindings shim. Runs on system Electron.
